<template>
    <button class="btn">{{ text }}
    </button>
</template>

<script>
     export default {
        name: "Button",
        props: {
            text: {
                type: String
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<style>
    .btn {
        /* outline: 1px orange solid; */
        width: 200px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: black;
    }

    .btn .btn-text {
        color: white
    }
</style>
